#txilu-pizzas-ts-api
this is one of my self projects about backend servers or api


#Description
In this project I created a node.js server with TypeScript and POO, and support connection with sql database 
 
#Tecnologies
 => Node.js
 => TypeScript
 => Sequelize.js (ORM)
 => SQL
 
#How to use
very simple!

  #1 install the dependices
    npm i
  #2 Run 
    npm start

#What now?
  you can send request to api : )